title: Le Crobag - Prenzlauer Allee
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, French, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chain bakery branch in the S-Bahn Prenzlauer Allee station. Sells baked goods, sandwiches, and hot drinks. Offers vegan baguettes filled with either tofu, basil and tomato, or herb spread and cucumber.
